# Project Structure

- The main application code is in the [app](mdc:app) directory at the root (not under `src`).
- Subdirectories include [(auth)](mdc:app/(auth)), [dashboard](mdc:app/dashboard), and [tests/[testId]](mdc:app/tests/[testId]) under [app](mdc:app).
- Shared React components are in [components](mdc:components).
- React context is in [context](mdc:context).
- Utility functions are in [utils](mdc:utils).
- Third-party integrations and API clients are in [lib](mdc:lib).
- Static assets are in [public](mdc:public).
